track_notes:
Park in town at big parking next to river. Signpost is right there stating 8h roundtour. That is about correct including about 1250 m acend and descend.
From Brettkogel to Wilder JÃ¤ger some section with steel cables - black difficulty T4.
Beautiful hike then over to summit with incredible views all around.
On the way down (or if you go in reverse) stop at Angerkaralm (hut) for drinks, small meals and great cake (summer season).

Summit has plenty of space but apart from summitcross nothing to mount antennas on. Bring a guying set and pegs for the mast.
track_title: Round trip via Neualm, Brettkogel to summit, T4
